    "The analysis of author productivity identified Zengin, Y., and Lavicsa, Z. as the most prolific authors, with 13 and 10 publications respectively.",
    "Notably, Zengin, Y. achieved the highest citation impact, with 189 citations across 13 articles, followed by Hohenwarter, M., who accumulated 187 citations from 5 articles.",
    "Among the 154 scholarly periodicals identified, the \"International Journal of Mathematical Education in Science and Technology\" emerged as the leading publisher, with 33 articles on GeoGebra.",
